        reason: >-
          CVE-2023-22622 (wp-cron.php DoS). No fixed version exists; mitigated at
          the server/edge layer by blocking direct access to wp-cron.php.
          Tracking: hametuha/hametuha-infra#19
        expires: 2027-07-23T00:00:00.000Z
patch: {}
